<db:titleabbrev>Qt 3D Reference Documentation</db:titleabbrev>
<db:abstract>
<db:para>Delegates mouse events to the attached <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-input-mousehandler.xml">MouseHandler</db:link> objects.</db:para>
<db:para>This type was introduced in Qt 5.5.</db:para>
</db:abstract>
